%% state_08_project_status.mmd — Project Status
%% Ref: project model (status: pending/in_progress/completed/cancelled)
%% ⚠️ Status transitions are NOT enforced in code
%% UpdateProjectCommand allows any status change (no state machine)

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : Project created

    pending --> in_progress : Work begins
    pending --> cancelled : Project cancelled

    in_progress --> completed : All tasks done
    in_progress --> cancelled : Project cancelled
    in_progress --> pending : Paused / reverted

    completed --> [*]
    cancelled --> pending : Reopened

    note right of pending
        ⚠️ These transitions are NOT enforced in code.
        UpdateProjectCommand accepts any status value.
        State machine shown here is the INTENDED workflow.
        ──────────────────
        Project visibility: public / private / internal
        allow_freelancer: enables marketplace for tasks
    end note

    note left of completed
        Completion does NOT auto-trigger
        anything at project level.
        Reviews are per-task, not per-project.
    end note
